                        <interp inst="t18720108-name-233" type="given" value="NENILA"></interp>NENILA PANTALIEF</persName>
                  </hi>. I am cook in Mr. Lassoto's service—on the morning of the 7th December I came down at 6 o'clock, and found all the front doors open, and three coats were missing—these are the coats—also four knives and 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., my money.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
